 basket|bread box|bread cake|bread crumb|bread sandwich|bread soda|bread-and-butter|bread-and-butter issue|bread-and-butter letter|bread-and-butter note|bread-and-butter pickle|bread-and-butter pudding|bread-and-cheese|bread-monger|burn bread|cockle-bread|coco bread|crazy bread|cuckoo's bread|cuckoo-bread|dain-bread|devil's bread|dog bread|dog-bread|don't get your meat where you get your bread|eaten bread is soon forgotten|Essene bread|Ezekiel bread|freedom bread|greatest thing since sliced bread|gut bread|gut-bread|half a loaf is better than no bread|hard dough bread|hardo bread|hot bread kitchen|kaffir bread|kafir bread|lamb's bread|lardy bread|man shall not live by bread alone|Molotov bread basket|Molotov's bread basket|monkey-bread|music bread|oven bread|prosciutto bread|put bread on the table|put butter on one's bread|sandwich bread|bread slicer|shew bread|sprouted bread|tea bread|treacle bread|Turkish bread|white-bread|Yule bread}}\n\n=====Descendants=====\n{{top4}}\n* {{desc|bi|bred}}\n** {{desc|bor=1|nmb|p'ret}}\n* {{desctree|srn|brede}}\n* {{desc|tpi|bret}}\n* {{desc|bor=1|hif|bareed}}\n* {{desc|bor=1|ha|burodi}}\n* {{desc|bor=1|ml|ബ്രെഡ്|alts=1}}\n* {{desc|bor=1|mh|būreej}}\n* {{desc|bor=1|nup|bureedi|qq=possibly via Hausa}}\n* {{desc|bor=1|ta|பிரெட்|பிரட்}}\n* {{desc|bor=1|yo|búrẹ́dì}}\n{{bottom}}\n\n=====Translations=====\n{{trans-top|baked dough made from cereals}}\n{{multitrans|data=\n* Abkhaz: {{tt|ab|амгьал}}, {{tt|ab|ача}}\n* Afar: {{tt|aa|gaqambo}}\n* Afrikaans: {{tt+|af|brood}}\n* Ainu: {{tt|ain|パン|tr=pan}}, {{tt|ain|ヘリェバ|tr=heryeba}}\n* Akkadian: {{tt|akk|𒃻|ts=ak(a)lu|tr=NINDA}}\n* Albanian: {{tt+|sq|bukë|f}}\n* Altai:\n*: Northern Altai: {{tt|atv|этпек|alt=этпе́к}}, {{tt|atv|ӧтпӧк}}, {{t|atv|калач}}\n*: Southern Altai: {{tt|alt|ӧтпӧк}}, {{tt|alt|калаш|alt=ка́ла́ш}}\n* Alutiiq: {{tt|ems|kelipaq}}\n* Ambonese Malay: {{tt|abs|roti}}\n* Amharic: {{tt|am|ዳቦ}}\n* Arabic: {{tt+|ar|خُبْز|m}}\n*: Algerian Arabic: {{tt|arq|خُبْز|tr=ḵobz}}, {{tt|arq|أغروم|